Entries.default: "What a mess. This is why wizards get a bad reputation."
"Hey, is that an orlan cage in back? They don't let you have those in Dyrwood anymore. That one's in pretty good condition."
"Magic shop, huh? I know a thing or two about making pirates disappear."
"Were I to be taking half this back to the Sorcerer, she'd truly live up the name."
"What a stifling little den. Do all wizards hate natural light?"
"Arkemyr's Auspicious Apples... Lets you see three seconds into the future. Hm."
"I've visited troll dens more hospitable'n this."
